00:02:38.346 --> 00:02:40.830
You know, a scientific result
doesn't mean anything unless

00:02:40.830 --> 00:02:42.580
you can convince
the community.

00:02:42.580 --> 00:02:45.730
So it's an inherently human
activity to bring people's

00:02:45.730 --> 00:02:48.240
attention to things,
make things clear.

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:50.400
Anyway, that was kind of cool.

